{"tid":1957640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普與疾控中心打對台 表明不戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T15:44:53.000Z","uid":201732,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f0334133cb1759eff4eedd6cf008fe50bce8a7f3","tid":1957640,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"他謂：「你毋須一定這樣做。我自己就選擇不會這樣做」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「我只是不想戴口罩，這只是一個建議。坐在圓橢形辦公室美麗的堅毅桌（總統辦公桌）後面，偉大的堅毅桌，接見其他國家的總統、總理、獨裁者、國皇和皇后，我不認為我要這樣做，或許我將來會改變主意。」<br />\n<br />\n當特朗普向記者發表講話時，站在他身旁的副總統彭斯以及在場的其他官員，都沒有戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LmRA3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LmRA3s.jpg&h=a53d2885&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45501e4056c97b26febc465b9d1a2b9569136174","tid":1957640,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200404/SOJNPPQDYFZNXODZWIPT6X6ACY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200404%2FSOJNPPQDYFZNXODZWIPT6X6ACY%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=f00e8b38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200404%2FSOJNPPQDYFZNXODZWIPT6X6ACY%2F&h=2bebff6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200404/SOJNPPQDYFZNXODZWIPT6X6ACY/</a><br />\n<br />\nCDC建議美國人外出戴布口罩 特朗普：我不會跟從"},{"pid":"8e333715acc81755e9fc1e8e90fe9185c8c49ee5","tid":1957640,"uid":3204,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"因為睇左陳云fb"},{"pid":"1c6cf72599bd651bdc3203df62429ec15f80c21e","tid":1957640,"uid":46493,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"條友係唔係以色列間諜，佢做既野有時睇唔出係為美國好"},{"pid":"08de9619e6398112474817d67bdcc05041b6bbb4","tid":1957640,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime